.span-14
  %h2
    So what is
    = flickrify("memoizr") + "?"
  %p
    Remember the game called "Memory" or "Concentration"? Now with 21st century technology You can relive that magic! Using infinite number of photos from 
    = flickrify("flickr") 
    you can spend rest of your life playing this wonderful game.


  %h2
    Wanna
    = flickrify("try") + "?"

  = form_for(:game, @game, :url => game_path, :method => :post, :html => { :class => 'clear' }) do |f|
    = f.label :images_category
    %br
    = f.text_field :images_category
    = @game.errors[:images_category]
    %br
    = f.submit 'Start a new game'

